reviewText: It's a strange tale , stolen jewelry, a insurance lawyer, gangster's , a former lover, a person who lovers him, an stranger of who how it was done, would leave you guessing. You might have to watch it again!
One of THE best movies I have seen in a long time.  I am so glad I brought this movie!!
DVD arrive in fine shape n plays grate. It's a fine movie n the hole family  can watch it.

A bit of Film-Noir mixed with Drama.  Barry Sullivan has the lead.  I always liked Barry Sullivan.  Richard Anderson as Detective Walter O'Bannion is in here as well.

It's mainly about an insurance scam.
